    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. It\u2019s been my reliable daily driver and has been kept in really solid shape\u2014just a few minor beauty marks that show it\u2019s actually been loved and driven. It runs like a dream and catches eyes at every light. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee and I\u2019ll hand you the keys for a spin!",
