    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This isn't your standard commuter; it\u2019s a precision-engineered machine dialed in for the discerning driver. The heart of this build features a high-compression powertrain with a remapped ECU optimized for linear power delivery across the entire rev range. I\u2019ve ensured the drivetrain remains rock-solid with reinforced bushings and a short-throw shifter that delivers mechanical, bolt-action precision. The suspension geometry has been fine-tuned to eliminate body roll without compromising high-speed stability, while the upgraded braking system provides exceptional thermal dissipation for consistent bite. Meticulously maintained with a focus on preventative lubrication and cooling efficiency, this car is ready to dominate both the apex and the open road.",
