    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you carve through coastal bends, the engine singing a soulful baritone that only decades of experience can perfect. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule of elegance and raw mechanical spirit. Every crease in the leather and every hum of the motor tells a story of weekend escapes and midnight drives. It possesses a certain gravitas, a seasoned poise that modern, plastic-wrapped vehicles simply cannot replicate. It\u2019s ready for its next chapter\u2014are you the one to write it?",
