    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my go-to for weekend getaways and morning coffee runs, and it\u2019s never let me down. It\u2019s got that wonderful 'just right' feel\u2014well-loved with a bit of character that tells a story, but still looking sharp and running smooth. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable ride with a soul, you\u2019ve found it! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive.",
